6- Opt-out
You can choose to prevent your device's ad identifier being used for interest-based advertising, or you can reset your device's ad identifier, by changing the settings of your device. See
optout.networkadvertising.org
for details.
The collection of personal data in the app by Tasmanic Editions and its Analytics & Marketing partners depends on your consent through a 'pop-up' shown at the first launch of the app.
You can give or withdraw your consent at anytime in the app itself : in the menu on the main page, open the 'privacy settings'.
For each purpose, you can select 'On' to allow the collection of personal data or 'Off' to disallow the collection of personal data.
Click 'OK' to submit your new settings.
Then force the app to close  (
more info
)
Then restart the app.
You can also contact our partners directly to ask for a full opt out or deletion of your data from their services, with the links provided above. You can also click on the AdChoices logo within an advertisement (where available).
